#. type: Plain text
#: 2020-04-07-newsletter-38.md:339
msgid ""
"“We are only as safe as our most vulnerable. The poor suffer most in both "
"crises and we urgently need to address **health and social inequalities**. "
"Global challenges need systemic change."
msgstr ""
"“Hoy somos todos igual de vulnerables. Los pobres sufren más en ambas crisis "
"y debemos afrontar urgentemente las **desigualdades sanitarias y sociales**. "
"Los retos globales requieren cambios sistémicos."

#. type: Plain text
#: 2020-04-07-newsletter-38.md:341
msgid ""
"Neither Covid nor climate pay attention to borders, the world is a small "
"place, and we're all interconnected. This is the basis of planetary health. "
"**Prevention is better than cure**."
msgstr ""
"Ni la COVID-19 ni la crisis climática entienden de fronteras, el mundo es un "
"lugar pequeño y todos estamos interconectados. Esta es la base de la salud "
"planetaria. **Más vale prevenir que curar**."

#. type: Plain text
#: 2020-04-07-newsletter-38.md:343
msgid ""
"The role and crucial importance of scientific expertise needs to be, and has "
"been, recognised. The cynicism and disregard for scientific expertise "
"promoted by populist politicians has hopefully lost credibility. People are "
"learning to trust and to value health and science professionals.”"
msgstr ""
"Debemos reconocer, y así ha sido, el rol y la crucial relevancia del "
"conocimiento científico. Parece que el cinismo y la desconsideración hacia "
"la ciencia de los políticos populistas ha perdido credibilidad. La gente "
"está aprendiendo a valorar y a confiar en los profesionales de la salud y de "
"la ciencia”."

#. type: Plain text
#: 2020-04-07-newsletter-38.md:345
#, no-wrap
msgid "*We are receiving amazing human stories and we want to know yours. To read more – or to write your own – join our* *[Facebook group](https://www.facebook.com/groups/468678977056685/)*.\n"
msgstr "*Estamos recibiendo historias humanas increíbles y queremos conocer la tuya. Para leer más historias o escribir la tuya, únete a nuestro* *[grupo de Facebook](https://www.facebook.com/groups/468678977056685/)*.\n"

